  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation of OpenSSL</title>

    <para>Prepare OpenSSL for compilation:</para>

<screen><userinput>sed 's/^passwd/openssl-passwd/' doc/apps/passwd.pod > doc/apps/openssl-passwd.pod
rm doc/apps/passwd.pod
mv doc/crypto/{,openssl_}threads.pod
./config --openssldir=/etc/ssl --prefix=/usr shared
sed -i 's%SHLIBDIRS= fips crypto ssl%SHLIBDIRS= crypto ssl%g' Makefile</userinput></screen>

    <para>Compile the package:</para>

<screen><userinput>make MANDIR=/usr/share/man</userinput></screen>

    <para>Install the package:</para>

<screen><userinput>make MANDIR=/usr/share/man install
cp -r certs /etc/ssl</userinput></screen>

